"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-29-Hungarian-judo-star-fights-for-his-sport-at-Olympics-1vBY2KMzSIo-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pablo Gutierrez in Budapest  Copied  Hungary's judo team wants gold medals at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999960757577, \"rank\": 3.921228884001956e-09, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.999984034656909, \"rank\": 1.297701496558236e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not have to see it to believe it.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You just have to listen.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The grunts, puffs and heaves spill into the streets around the training center in Budapest.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999960757577, \"rank\": 3.921228884001956e-09, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team has not had much to shout about over the last few years, but these athletes are determined to 'pump up the volume' in Paris.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999534213668, \"rank\": 4.65786487397274e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hungary sent a team of seven judokas to this year's Games.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.999984034656909, \"rank\": 1.297701496558236e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The standout performer is Krisztian Toth, who won bronze at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8172513466538323, \"rank\": 0.22329677166492265, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very tired, of course, but we are on the right path,\\\" says Toth.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are doing everything possible to be in great shape for the Games.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Overall, I am feeling very positive.\\\"\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Krisztian Toth (blue clothes) is aiming for Hungary's first gold in an Olympic judo event since 1992.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.999984034656909, \"rank\": 1.297701496558236e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CGTN Europe  The 30-year-old is looking to become the first Hungarian to win two judo medals at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.999450922750867, \"rank\": 0.0004814497562589852, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says he will not be happy with anything short of gold.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am determined to return from Paris as an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999534213668, \"rank\": 4.65786487397274e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a huge dream.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have set high standards for myself, but I am determined to achieve them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hungary has won 10 Olympic medals in judo, but it's only secured one gold.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.999984034656909, \"rank\": 1.297701496558236e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Toth's coach, Gabor Panczel, says he has a good chance of adding to that tally.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Gabor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.882434260108933e-14, \"text\": \"Gabor\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Gabor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Gabor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is plenty of pressure, because a poor performance could prove costly.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"Every Olympics is crucial for the Hungarian Judo Association,\\\" says Panczel.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Judo_Association\", \"score\": 0.999999999642796, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hungarian Judo Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Judo_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_Judo_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We face economic challenges, and sports that do not make profits tend to struggle.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This Olympics is a double test for us as our future depends on our performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel incredibly fortunate,\\\" says Toth.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My Olympic medals have opened many doors for me.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited to see what the future holds.\\\"\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba